</div>
<div>
<p>　　孝宗<num value="2">二</num>女<pc>：</pc>長嘉國公主<pc>，</pc>紹興<measure quantity="24" unit="years">
<num value="24">二十四</num>年</measure>
<pc>，</pc>封碩人<pc>，</pc>進永嘉郡主<pc>，</pc>
<measure quantity="32" unit="years">
<num value="32">三十二</num>年</measure>卒<pc>。</pc>詔以醫官李師克等屬吏<pc>，</pc>孝宗時居東宮<pc>，</pc>奏<pc>：</pc>
